    scene expression 'background/CMO_05.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "Back then, the whole mansion was like a giant playground."
    
    "The garden, a deep forest."
    
    "The house, a tall castle."
    
    "We played in our own little world, which would take days to explore."
    
    "Every day was fun."
    
    "No one thought about ever growing up,"
    
    "and we believed that days and nights would always be the same."
    
    "It was just a childhood spent playing like puppies."
    
    "We got along wonderfully, and were the best of playmates."
    
    "Whenever I turned back, Akiha would be there, aacing her hands and hiding shyly."
    
    "Yes, always the same."
    
    "At that time, the mansion was a giant playground."
    
    "The garden, a deep forest."
    
    "The house, a tall castle."
    
    "We played in our own little world, which would take days to explore."
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_11.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "I slowly awaken and open my eyes."
    
    "The morning light wraps around me and my sleepiness starts to lift."
    
    "As the last vestiges clear,"
    
    "I sense that I had a very nostalgic dream."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40E.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "\"-------\""
    
    "As soon as I open my eyes, I start to see those terrible things jump into my vision."
    
    "My head stabs with pain."
    
    "\"Gg----\""
    
    "I scramble for the glasses by my pillow and put them on."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    play music 'sound/02.mp3'
    
    "I take in some air."
    
    "After taking a few deep breaths, I manage to calm down."
    
    "\"Why did I---so early..\""
    
    "See those lines so clearly this early in the morning?"
    
    "It's difficult to see the lines of death in buildings."
    
    "It's usually hard to see them, and seeing them so clearly like I just did now is rare."
    
    "\"........\""
    
    "What's more, I even saw those \"points\"."
    
    "I think my headache is getting worse too."
    
    "Sensei said these eyes would attract things that weren't good."
    
    "I think Arcueid and these vampires are certainly not good."
    
    "So, maybe it's all affecting my eyes and making them stronger."
    
    "\"----Can't be.\""
    
    "I'm probably just tired."
    
    "\"Please excuse me.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T01.png' as i0 at fgpos(62, 0)
    
    "Hisui enters, greeting me with a bow."
    
    "\"Ah, morning Hisui.\""
    
    "\"Yes, good morning Shiki-sama.\""
    
    ".... Hisui brings my uniform as usual."
    
    "But what is it?"
    
    "I think she is a bit angry."
    
    "\"Hisui, did something happen this morning?"
    
    "You seem, to be in a bad mood.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T08.png' as i0 at fgpos(62, 0)
    
    "\"............\""
    
    "Hisui looks at me as though she wants to say something, and then walks silently to the door."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T01.png' as i0 at fgpos(62, 0)
    
    "\"Then please excuse me."
    
    "I will tell Nee-san to prepare your breakfast, so please hurry to the sitting room.\""
    
    "\"Yeah, I planned on doing so....\""
    
    "I am a bit curious why Hisui is mad."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T09.png' as i0 at fgpos(62, 0)
    
    "\" I forgot to say one thing."
    
    "Akiha-sama would like to talk to you about your sneaking out last night."
    
    "So please hurry to the sitting room.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_40A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "She shuts the door emotionlessly."
    
    "\"Cr-----\""
    
    "Crap."
    
    "They know about me sneaking out last night."
    
    "\".... Go to the sitting room means Akiha is waiting there....?\""
    
    "Man.... Why can't bad things be just kept a secret?"
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "Akiha is the only one in the sitting room."
    
    "Kohaku-san is in the kitchen, humming away."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T11A.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\"............\""
    
    "Akiha doesn't say anything when she sees me and sips her tea quietly."
    
    "\"Hey."
    
    "Good morning, Akiha.\""
    
    "I try to greet her as naturally as I can."
    
    "Akiha's eyebrow twitches as she places her teacup down and slowly looks at me."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T18A.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\"Good morning Nii-san."
    
    "It was quite late when you came home last night, wasn't it?\""
    
    "\".... No, not really."
    
    "It was at most a little past one o'clock, quite normal for a healthy young man in high school to be up, right?\""
    
    "\"I see."
    
    "My bedtime is also past midnight so I was up at that time."
    
    "But I would come home much earlier than that.\""
    
    "\"Yeah, even I was home earlier, wasn't I?"
    
    ".... I just had something to do, so I was out for a little bit---\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T11A.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\"Without permission?"
    
    "You acted like you were out doing something you felt guilty over.\""
    
    "\"Uh....\""
    
    "Her stare is pure ice."
    
    ".... This is the second time, and I'm sure even though Akiha looks calm, she is quite angry."
    
    "\"--Nii-san."
    
    "I don't know what went on at the Arima house, but here the curfew is eight o'clock."
    
    "It is a rule that must not be broken."
    
    "The gate will be locked after that, so please don't climb in like a robber.\""
    
    "\"Oh---You knew?\""
    
    "\".... The surveillance camera showed me quite clearly."
    
    "It is a good thing Kohaku-san realized it was you and turned off the alarm system because otherwise you would probably be detained right now, Tohno Shiki.\""
    
    "\".... Oh."
    
    "I should thank Kohaku-san then."
    
    "And, um, Akiha, I'm sorry."
    
    "I shouldn't have kept quiet about it.\""
    
    "\".... If you understand, then it is fine."
    
    "Please make sure you observe your curfew from now on."
    
    "I will overlook it this time.\""
    
    "\".... About that, Akiha.\""
    
    "\"What is it?\""
    
    "\".... This is a little hard to say."
    
    "I.. have something to do tonight too."
    
    "I don't know when I will be back, but I'm not going to do anything bad---\""
    
    "\"---------\""
    
    "Akiha's gaze tightens."
    
    "\"Kohaku!\""
    
    "She suddenly stands up."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "Kohaku-san comes in from the kitchen."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/KOHA_T02.png' as i0 at fgpos(-12, 0)
    
    "\"Yes, what is it Akiha-sama?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/KOHA_T02.png' as i0 at fgpos(-12, 0)
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T11A.png' as i1 at fgpos(104, 0)
    
    "\"I will be going to school, get the preparations ready.\""
    
    "\"Huh?"
    
    "But I have not yet made Shiki-san's breakfast.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/KOHA_T02.png' as i0 at fgpos(-12, 0)
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T06.png' as i1 at fgpos(104, 0)
    
    "\"You can leave this person alone."
    
    "It seems he can do everything by himself.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/KOHA_T02.png' as i0 at fgpos(-12, 0)
    
    "Akiha strides towards the lobby."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/KOHA_T01A.png' as i0 at fgpos(-12, 0)
    
    "Kohaku-san sighs."
    
    "\".... Shiki-san, you should not make Akiha-sama so upset."
    
    "You are her big brother, so please treat her better okay?\""
    
    "Saying that, she walks after Akiha."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "The teacup sits, still steaming."
    
    "\"---Well, in short..\""
    
    "I'm left by myself to calmly consider my situation."
    
    "\"I guess I'm skipping breakfast today.\""
    
    "Yeah, no doubt."
    
    ".... I should stop by a convenience store on the way and buy some bread."
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    stop music
    
